data.description: Here's a chance to invest your effort and creativity in this spacious raised rancher. The main floor features three generously sized bedrooms, including a primary bedroom with a private bath, a shared hallway bathroom, a roomy eat-in kitchen, a sunroom with access to the rear yard, and a living room. The partially finished lower level offers flexibility with a family room that could potentially serve as a fourth bedroom, a bathroom, a storage closet, a workshop area, and convenient garage access. With a generous yard, a lovely front deck, and ample parking, this residence offers both space and potential. While some tender loving care is needed, this home eagerly awaits the transformative touch of your personal style. Seize the opportunity to make this property uniquely yours!
